@mainpage Cloud Identity-Aware Proxy API C++ Client Library

An idiomatic C++ client library for the [Cloud Identity-Aware Proxy API][cloud-service-docs],
a service to control access to applications running on Google Cloud Platform.

While this library is **GA**, please note Google Cloud C++ client libraries do **not** follow [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/).

